quran[8{c,v,t}:
16,35,"yeh mushriqeen kehte hain"" agar Allah chahta to nah hum aur nah hamaray baap dada uss ke siwa kisi aur ki ibadat karte aur nah uss ke hukum ke baghair kisi cheez ko haraamtehratay"" aisay hi bahanay inn se pehlay ke log bhi banatay rahay hain to kya Rasolo-n par saaf saaf baat pouncha dainay ke siwa aur bhi koi zimma daari hai ?"
16,36,"hum ne har ummat mein aik rasool bhaij diya, aur uss ke zareya se sab ko khabardaar kar diya ke"" Allah ki bandagi karo aur Taghoot ki bandagi se bachcho"" is ke baad un mein se kisi ko Allah ne hadaayat bakhsh aur kisi par zallatmusallat ho gayi phir zara zameen mein chal phir kar dekh lau ke jhutlanay walon ka kya injaam ho chuka hai"
16,37,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum chahay inn ki hadaayat ke liye kitney hi harees ho, magar Allah jis ko bhatka deta hai phir usay hadaayat nahi diya karta aur is terhan ke logon ki madad koi nahi kar sakta"
16,38,"yeh log Allah ke naam se kari kari kasmain kha kar kehte hain ke"" Allah kisi marnay walay ko phir se zindah kar ke nah uthaye ga"" uthaye ga kyun nahi, yeh to aik wada hai jisay poora karna is ne apne oopar wajib kar liya hai, magar aksar log jantay nahi hain"
16,39,aur aisa hona is liye zurori hai ke Allah inn ke samnay uss haqeeqat ko khol day jis ke baray mein yeh ikhtilaaf kar rahay hain aur munkareen haq ko maloom ho jaye ke woh jhutay thay
16,40,"( raha is ka imkaan to ) hamein kisi cheez ko wujood mein laane ke liye is se ziyada kuch karna nahi hota ke usay hukum den"" ho ja"" aur bas woh ho jati hai"
16,41,jo log zulm sehney ke baad Allah ki khatir hijrat kar gay hain un ko hum duniya hi mein acha thikana den ge aur akhirat ka ajar to bohat bara hai kash jaan len woh mazloom
16,42,jinhon ne sabr kya hai aur jo apne rab ke bharoosay par kaam kar rahay hain ( ke kaisa acha injaam unn ka muntazir hai )
